import { BarChart,Bar,Rectangle,XAxis,YAxis,CartesianGrid,Tooltip,Legend,ResponsiveContainer } from "recharts";

function Bars ({input}) {
    let data = input

    return input && (
        <ResponsiveContainer width="80%" height={320}>
            <BarChart data={data} margin={{top: 5,right: 30, left: 20, bottom: 5,}} barGap='10%'>
                <CartesianGrid strokeDasharray="3 3" vertical={false}/>
                <XAxis dataKey={input.key} tickFormatter={(tick)=> tick +1}/>
                <YAxis dataKey="kilogram" yAxisId={"kg"} type="number" scale={"sequential"} domain={['dataMin - 1','dataMax +1']} allowDecimals={false} orientation="right" axisLine={false} tickLine={false}/>
                <YAxis dataKey="calories" yAxisId={"cal"} type="number" hide={true} domain={['dataMin - 50','dataMax + 50']}/>
                <Tooltip />
                <Legend iconType="circle"/>
                <Bar dataKey="kilogram" yAxisId={"kg"} fill="#282D30" radius={[10,10,0,0]} barSize={9} activeBar={<Rectangle fill="#282D30" stroke="#282D30" />} />
                <Bar dataKey="calories" yAxisId={"cal"} fill="#E60000" radius={[10,10,0,0]} barSize={9} activeBar={<Rectangle fill="#E60000" stroke="#E60000" />} />
            </BarChart>
        </ResponsiveContainer>
    )
}

export default Bars
